{"tid":2358110,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國增53宗武漢肺炎確診，33宗屬河北本土個案，封城第一天實況影像！","createTime":"2021-01-08T01:58:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T02:04:30.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"027b5daee8ecd27f80b707528698c62666797093","tid":2358110,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T01:58:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xL1Y6f0HeB8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxL1Y6f0HeB8&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIfUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=56a0918c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xL1Y6f0HeB8</a><br />\n<br />\n中國過去一日新增53宗武漢肺炎確診個案，當中37宗的本土病例中，有33宗來自河北，遼寧有兩宗，北京、黑龍江各有一宗本土個案。至於其餘16宗輸入病例，分別來自上海、廣東、江蘇等。<br />\n<br />\n中國至今一共有87331宗確診個案，單日無新增死亡與疑似病例。另外，中國單日新增57名無症狀感染者。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569285-20210108.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569285-20210108.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIfUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=bbeab741\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569285-20210108.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=fa08d4e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569285-20210108.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"b672368612a99a3dcbbfa3d7148fcee6a017b654","tid":2358110,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T02:04:30.000Z","msg":"其他國家又爆發"}]}